            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro salute <lb n="2"/>domus divi<lb break="no" n="3"/>nae sacrum <lb n="4"/>Genium <note>sic</note> Miciae <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Cornelius <lb n="6"/>Stratonicus <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>et ante <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>rontem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>lapi</abbr><ex>dibus</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>stravit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der linken Nebenseite patera, auf der rechten urceus. Hederae in Z. 7 und 9. (B): Daicoviciu; AE 1931; AE 1933: Z. 2: div[i].</p>
            </div>
